==== Bhartacho dhavo prodhanomontri ====

Bhartacho dhavo prodhanomontri. Tacho bapuy krixnn bihari vajpeyi prosid'd lekhok ani kovi. Tache auychem namv krixnnadevi.
Atal Bihari Vajpayee, 2002.

Atal Bihari Vajpeyin gvaliyroche vikttoria kealejintlean bi. E. Podvi ghetli. Uprant kanpuroche ddi.E.Vi. Kealejintlean tannem rajnitik xastrant em'.E. Podvi melloili. Tannem kaideachoi obheas kela. Tannem somaz seuk ani potrokar mhonnunoi vaur kela. 1942 to bharti-i svatontry cholloullint vantto ghetil'lo mhunn taka bondkhonnichi kheast favo zal'li. 1941 to ottol raxttri-i svoimseuk songhak mell'llo. Tannem raxttrodhrm' (mhoinallem), panchojny (satollem) toxench svodex ani vir orzun hea disalleanchem sompadon kelam.

====Bharti-i zon songh====

Atal Bihari Vajpeyin 1951 to bharti-i zon songhachi sthapnnuk keli. 1957 to to dusre loksobhecher venchun ailo. 1957 te 77 meren tannem bharti-i zonsongh parlomenttori partticho mukheli mhunn vaur kela. 1962 to to rajyosobhecho vangddi zalo. 1967 to to portun loksobhecher venchun ailo. 1968 te 73 meren bharti-i zon songhacho odhyokx, 1971, 1977 ani 1980 to loksobhecher portun to venchun ailo. 1980 te 1986 meren to bharti-i zonta partticho odhyokx aslo. 1986 te 1981 meren to portun rajy sobhecho vangddi aslo. 1986 to taka bharti-i zonta parttichea somsdi-i pongddacho mukheli mhunn venchun kaddlo. 1991 to to portun loksobhecher venchun ailo. 1991 - 93 meren to poblik okamutt komitticho odhyokx aslo. 1996 to to satvi khep loksobhecher venchun ailo. Te loksobheche venchnnukent bharti-i zonta parttiche soglleant chodd (164) vangddi venchun aile. Haka lagun raxttropoti xonkor doyal xorman bharti-i zonta partticho odhyokx ottol bihari vajpeyik prodhanomontri podacho sopun dilo ani tera disambhitor taka bhoumot sidhd korpak lailem. Punn her pokxamni taka tenko divonk naxil'lean tannem tera disamnich aplea podacho rajinamo dilo. 1996 - 97 meren tannem loksobhent virodhi pokxacho mukheli mhunn kam' polloilem. 1998 to to loksobhecher atthve khep venchun ailo. 19 march 1998 disa to portun prodhanomontri zalo.

====Kovi====

Atal Bihari vajpeyi ho ek prosid'd kovi asun tache mrityu ya hot'tea, omor bolidan, koidi kovirai ki kunddliam, omor ag hoi ani meri ekeavon kovitayem he kovita jhele prosid'd asat. Tannem raxttrakhatir kel'lea vaurak lagun taka raxttropotin podm' vibhuxonn purskar bhettoila. Toxench 1994 to taka lokmany ttillok purskar, bharot rotn, pom. Govind pont purskar mell'lleat.


